# Website deploy workflow

The marketing site lives in `website/` and deploys via Vercel from GitHub (`main`).

After completing any change under `website/`:

1. Stage only website-related files (and this rule if changed): `git add website/`
2. Commit with a clear message focused on why (e.g. copy fix, remove dead links).
3. Push to `origin main`: `git push`

Do this in the same session as the website edit unless the user explicitly says not to push.

Do not commit build artifacts, secrets, or unrelated MAUI changes in the same commit unless the user asked for a combined push.

Remote: https://github.com/kaisynctech/KaiSyncWorkforce-App.git
